Builds the complete Universal Intent Sniper Workflow for the NEXUS platform:

Backend (nexus-be):
- 5 SQLAlchemy models: sniper_run, sniper_timeline, sniper_match, sniper_script, sniper_action
- 2 Pydantic v2 schema files (sniper.py, sniper_actions.py)
- 13 services: orchestrator, normalizer, signal, targeting, query, search,
  source classifier, evidence gate, osiris rating, BANT qualification,
  magic scripting (CoreAI/template fallback), action service, timeline service
- FastAPI router with 8 endpoints under /api/v1/sniper
- SNIPER_INTEGRATION.md with main.py append instructions (non-destructive)

Frontend (nexus-fe):
- 19 components under src/components/intent-workflow/ including
  UniversalIntentWorkflowModal, FulfillmentTimeline, OsirisRatingPanel,
  QualificationScorePanel, MagicScriptingPanel, MatchedTargetsTable,
  MatchDetailDrawer, WorkflowActionsBar, and supporting panels
- 6 lib files: types.ts, api.ts, normalizers.ts, status.ts, mockObjects.ts, index.ts
- 6 hooks: useUniversalIntentWorkflow, useWorkflowTimeline, useSniperResults,
  useMagicScripting, useOsirisRating, useWorkflowActions
- Demo page at /demo/universal-intent-modal with 7 mock object launchers

